    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A shaman who selects the lore spirit appears far wiser and knowing that her age would suggest. Though she can seem unassuming, her eyes give the impression she is peering deep into all she looks at, seeing the secrets of the essential merely by concentrating.</em><br><br><strong>Spirit Magic Spells:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.llxrra87kbofmyhl]{Identify} (1st),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.m1rmcpcaixcpz9ib]{Tongues} (2nd),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.tcnirpnzjdaym1fd]{Locate Object} (3rd),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.b5mz8voksps5g4yq]{Legend Lore} (4th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.68ngvzmzvadhf6vs]{Contact Other Plane} (5th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.14chms7xurvi85x9]{Owl's Wisdom, Mass} (6th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.aqeaxoaozlv9vg35]{Vision} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.2vb5orfcy57lrfmc]{Moment of Prescience} (8th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.7mstq5c76h3e6zzx]{Time Stop} (9th)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Spirit Animal: </strong>The shamanâ€™s spirit animal appears to be quiet and unassuming. It gains a +2 bonus on Initiative checks and a +4 bonus on Stealth checks.</p>",
